-preparar/ingredients\">\r\n<div class=\"ingredient__details\" data-field=\"\" data-field-name=\"quantity_and_name\" data-field-hint=\"Hacer clic en Intro para añadir otro ingrediente\" data-placeholder=\"100 gr. harina\" data-maxlength=\"200\"><span class=\"ingredient__quantity\">1 Pizca</span> Pimienta</div></li>\r\n 	<li id=\"ingredient_4387338\" class=\"ingredient \" data-record=\"/co/recipes/528581-ensalada-dietetica-de-lechuga-y-tomate-facil-y-rapida-de-preparar/ingredients\">\r\n<div class=\"field-group--ingredient\" data-field-group=\"\">\r\n<p class=\"ingredient__details\" data-field-name=\"quantity_and_name\" data-field-hint=\"Hacer clic en Intro para añadir otro ingrediente\" data-placeholder=\"100 gr. harina\" data-maxlength=\"200\"><span class=\"ingredient__quantity\">1 Cucharada pequeña</span> Vinagre o Mostaza</p>\r\n\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</section><section id=\"steps\" class=\"steps-container document__panel__section\">\r\n<div class=\"document__title-container split-header\">\r\n<h2 class=\"document__title split-header__main\">Pasos</h2>\r\n<div class=\"split-header__secondary shrink-xs subtle\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div data-field-group=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"numbered-list__contents\">\r\n<div class=\"media step__description\">\r\n<div class=\"media__img-rev\">\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li class=\"step-image droppable\" data-field=\"image\" data-field-name=\"image_id\" data-ajax-upload=\"/co/step/images\">Pica el tomate y la lechuga (previamente lavados) como lo desees (julianas, cuadros, etc).</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"step-image droppable\" data-field=\"image\" data-field-name=\"image_id\" data-ajax-upload=\"/co/step/images\">Agrega la pimienta, el zumo del limón y el vinagre o mostaza.</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"step-image droppable\" data-field=\"image\" data-field-name=\"image_id\" data-ajax-upload=\"/co/step/images\">Revuelve bien los ingredientes y sirva.\r\n<div class=\"numbered-list__contents\">\r\n<div class=\"media step__description\">\r\n<div 